<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<%- include("./partials/head") %>

    <body>

        <%- include("./partials/header") %>

            <main class="body__main__login">
                <section class="body__main__login__section1">
                    <article class="body__main__login__section1__article1">
                        <h3>¡que lindo verte otra vez!</h3>
                        <p>Ingresando podrás ver el estado de tus órdenes, los productos guardados en tu Wishlist y tus
                            puntos
                            Amapola disponibles para canjearlos por descuentos.
                        </p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="body__main__login__section1__article2">
                        <form class="body__main__login__section1__article2__form" action="" method="POST">
                            <div>
                                <label for="email">correo electronico</label>
                                <input type="email" name="email" id="email">
                                <p class="text-danger">
                                    <%= locals.errors && errors.email ? errors.email.msg : null %>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label for="password">contraseña</label>
                                <input type="password" name="password" id="password">
                                <a href="">¿Olvidaste tu contraseña?</a>
                                <p class="text-danger">
                                    <%= locals.errors && errors.password ? errors.password.msg : null %>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="body__main__login__section1__article2__checkbox">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="remember" id="recordame">
                                <label for="recordame">Recordame</label><br>
                                <p class="text-danger"><%= locals.errors && errors.terms ? errors.terms.msg : null %></p>
                            </div> 

                            <button class="body__main__login__section1__article2__form--button"
                                type="submit">Ingresa</button>
                        </form>
                        <div class="body__main__login__section1__article2__div">
                            <a href="">Login <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook-square"></i></a>
                            <a href="">Login <i class="fa-brands fa-google"></i></a>
                        </div>
                        <form class="body__main__login__section1__article2__checkbox" action="">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="terminos" id="terminos">
                            <label for="terminos">By clicking of the social
                                login buttonsyou agree to the terms of privacity
                                policy described <a href="">here</a> </label>

                        </form>
                    </article>
                </section>
                <section class="body__main__login__section2">
                    <div class="body__main__login__section2--divlinea"></div>
                    <article class="body__main__login__section2__article1">
                        <h3>¿primera vez en <br> amapola bags?</h3>
                        <p>Creá tu cuenta, es grátis y podrás ganar puntos Amapola de muchas maneras, que luego
                            canjearás por
                            descuentos.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="body__main__login__section2__article2">
                        <div class="body__main__login__section2__article2__div">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-truck"></i>
                            <p>envios sin cargo a todo el pais</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="body__main__login__section2__article2__div">
                            <i class="fa-regular fa-credit-card"></i>
                            <p class="body__main__section2__article2__div--p1">¡3,6 y 12 cuotas sin interés todos los
                                dias!</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="body__main__login__section2__article2__div">
                            <i class="fa-regular fa-face-laugh-beam"></i>
                            <p>amapola club</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="body__main__login__section2__article2__div">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-store"></i>
                            <p class="body__main__login__section2__article2__div--p2">¡retiro en tienda en 2 hs!</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="body__main__login__section2__article2__div">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-arrow-left"></i>
                            <p>cambios y devoluciones sin cargo</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="body__main__login__section2__article2__div">
                            <i class="fa-regular fa-heart"></i>
                            <p class="body__main__login__section2__article2__div--p3">wishlist</p>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                    <div class="body__main__login__section2__div">
                        <a href="/users/register"> crear cuenta</a>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </main>

            <%- include("./partials/footer") %>

    </body>